Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:40.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:46.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:52.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:58.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:04.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:16.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:20.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:28.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:35.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.02,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当邪恶在此世蔓延之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会现身的希望之战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身着星座之圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发蕴藏在身体中的能量“小宇宙”进行着战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正是 保护大地上爱与和平的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士光牙寻找雅典娜的旅程还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同逃出Palaestra的海蛇座市会合后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的圣斗士们来到了土之遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时 市突然化身为水蛇座白银圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为玛尔斯的手下对光牙等人发动了进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗找到了白银圣斗士米开朗基罗的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏了核心 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了土之小宇宙水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而面对为了尊严而误入歧途的市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳再度爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙虽然很惦念市今后的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是继续向下一个遗迹进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年们 燃起内心的小宇宙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在命运的星辰之下！圣斗士们的生存之路！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途跋涉 又破坏了两个核心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很耗费精力和体力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起之前居住的岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个遗迹 在海的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火星士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再交给白银圣斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们火星士追击部队蚂蚁分队来打败你们吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败这些蚁类火星士 强行突破吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 必须要先考虑阿莉雅的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了 准备进攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉…拉辛斯基队长 这该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我追！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们跑了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来顺利摆脱他们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 趁现在快去港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人和车的密度是什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是光牙第一次来大都市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒 居然有这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多游客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说世界各地的风景名胜以及自然资源丰富的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是湖泊干涸就是花田枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 游客才会在这里集中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是因为巴比伦塔的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用为此多虑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是这艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正要启航了 真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有十分钟就要发船了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客请在这里买票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里付钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船就要开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生给的钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像丢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦 这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 上不了船也就无法继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想个法子才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船的话 还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以乘我的小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你倒是小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打碎的盘子钱 可是要从你的工钱里扣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我家开的食宿公寓（pension）Paulo&Anne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食宿公寓是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是提供住宿的地方       
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是一种给人居家感的宾馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老太婆 我刚带回来几个打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗…就这么几个小毛头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞出什么岔子我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里一直都是我和老太婆两个人忙活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近客人实在太多 忙得不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想让你们来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士可以打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会得到谅解的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为了拯救雅典娜而打的工啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好工作 我会给你们出船的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 美丽的女士们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店将为您提供上等美味佳肴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都要手洗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铆足干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这扫除做得跟杂耍似的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您点了咖啡欧蕾 柠檬茶 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及巧克力蛋糕两块对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我们没点蛋糕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我送给二位的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 点菜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 二位美女是从哪儿来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 又手滑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你到底要打碎多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不好好干 就给我滚蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅就不用了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子洗起盘子来才更得心应手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你好久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务生只有我一个 力有不逮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你力有不逮！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直在和女孩子聊天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 实在是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是刚来的新人 还没适应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝高了就早点回家睡觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗了半天还没完…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这也是为了能前往下一个遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力过大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 有飞贼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们别干了 究竟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难以启齿 不过有你们在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而增加我们的工作量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要炒我们鱿鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再给我们一次机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会用拿手的技法来取悦观众的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿手的技法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位女士们 先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paulo&Anne特别火焰料理秀开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩特制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷刷地加上调味料 请品尝吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子 那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到全体被炒鱿鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这下借船的事情还办的成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了给我们坐船作为打工的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都被解雇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们帮忙 店里反而更忙乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也不太方便开船出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 如何才能过海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人倒是轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明因为玛尔斯的关系 整个世界已经陷入危机了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不知道玛尔斯的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说玛尔斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家连圣斗士的存在都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不为人知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我住在小岛上的时候 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经听沙织小姐这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织小姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得接受圣斗士的训练不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人 都是沿着星辰所定的命运生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如有人是在幸福的星辰庇护下出生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人则生在不幸的星辰下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有各自有各种各样的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你是在圣斗士的星辰下出生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如沙织小姐所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我是在圣斗士的星辰庇护下出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗你们也一定都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上跟我们年纪差不多的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都享受着普通的青春 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开朗快乐的生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人生 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能痛苦又严苛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们要在圣斗士的星辰下 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是段感人肺腑的话啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是命中注定要在这里死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你们再逃个看看？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把这座城里的人全部杀掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要开始什么表演吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要波及旁人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚁分队 攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危 危险 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就说过　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的命运就是葬身于此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要死在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们是在圣斗士之星辰的指引下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼尽全力生活的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区…区区圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想赢过火星士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让他们见识一下我们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱行进 Hell's Proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈焰暴徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士流忍法 龟甲斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马闪光拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真棒　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是场精彩的演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很受感动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…演出是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是扣人心弦呐 着实让人大吃一惊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你们几个竟然是旅行艺人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然能让旅客这么高兴　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个再回来我的店里打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…都说了这不是演出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是场天大的误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下也给你们的旅店痛快地宣传了一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子 如果客人继续增加我们该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这次的报酬我们就不客气喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小店可是随时恭候的哟　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可一定要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 你们店一定要变成一个能吸引更多可爱妹子的旅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 我们总算能坐上船了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总觉得今天过得好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向火之遗迹进发的道路尽是溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行一边躲避敌人一边前行 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一位独行的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位少女懂得修复损伤圣衣的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是地狱犬座Cerberus的多莱却攻了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应守护之物！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣修复师与传说中的矿石！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受过小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
